40|$|In {{this paper}} {{results from a}} {{forthcoming}} paper are presented concerning the convexity of multivariate <b>spline</b> <b>functions</b> built from B-patches. Conditions are given under which it is possible todefi a control net for such <b>spline</b> <b>functions.</b> The control net is understood as a piecewise linear function. If it is convex, then so is the underlying spline. Keywords: multivariate splines, B-patches, convexity, control nets, Greville-abscissae. ...|$|R
